b singing Big Spender in a club but was fired after refusing to <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Striptease" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Striptease" target="_blank">strip</a> offShe <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Married..._with_Children" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Married..._with_Children" target="_blank">married</a> three more <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times" target="_blank">times</a> One husband was also <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder" target="_blank">killed</a> in a car crash and another <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" target="_blank">died</a> from an overdoseTry our quick news quiz below
